OL,7,FA former vet who drugged children with
OL,8,Fsweets at a summer camp before
OL,9,Fsexually assaulting them, and drugged
OL,10,Fhis wife so she would not wake while
OL,11,Fthe abuse took place, will be
OL,12,Fsentenced on Friday.
OL,14,FSummer camp leader Jon Ruben, 76,
OL,15,Flaced sweets with tranquillising drugs
