OL,7,FRuben, who ran a holiday camp for at
OL,8,Fleast 27 years, sobbed in the dock as
OL,9,Fhe pleaded guilty to administering a
OL,10,Fpoison or noxious substance `
OL,11,FTemazepam ` to Susan Ruben between
OL,12,FJuly 26 and 29 last year so she would
OL,13,Fnot wake up while he sexually
OL,14,Fassaulted the children.
OL,16,FRuben, of Wayte Court in Ruddington,
OL,17,FNottinghamshire, was arrested in July
OL,18,Flast year after a total of eight
OL,19,Fchildren were taken to hospital and
OL,20,Fliquid Xanax was found to have been
OL,21,Fused on some of the victims.
